        "created_at": "2025-03-13T03:27:00.786Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I have two friends on IOS whose Signal apps do not auto update. This is troubling as it would take me a while to realize that my friends may not be seeing the messages I am sending. It sometimes became as bad as 2-3 weeks before asking them via SMS if they were receiving my Signal texts. Both of them have auto-updates on in the app store. Is there a way for Signal to auto update for them like their other apps?</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 4,
        "updated_at": "2025-03-13T03:27:00.786Z",
