        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/ccd318/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2025-03-13T10:02:56.289Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hi,<br>\nThere seem to be two different issues here. The auto updating not working would probably be an iOS issue if it is enabled in the app store and it shows that new versions are available. The other issue is that, unless their version is really old, they should still be receiving your messages if they haven’t updated Signal in a while. Do you know which versions this is concerning?</p>",
