        "created_at": "2025-03-13T18:46:48.640Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I do not know which versions they were using prior to updating, and they probably did not know either. Looking back, I recognize that the one that took 2-3 weeks was because my friend got a new phone and didn’t log onto Signal yet. The most recent one did seem to be a result of Signal not updating for my friend, and I believe it started happening the 1st of March. My other friend similarly stopped receiving my messages on the 2nd of March. Both of my friends pointed to having to update Signal before they were able to see what I sent the past week or so.</p>",
